text: Hidekatsu Ishida (born 1908, died between 1940 and 1945) was a Japanese diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre platform event at the 1932 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1940s deaths Category:Japanese male divers Category:Olympic divers of Japan Category:Divers at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
